  &lt;messagepanel>
    &lt;typeofhazard>Rotating blade.&lt;/typeofhazard>
    &lt;consequence>Moving parts can crush and cut.&lt;/consequence>
    &lt;howtoavoid>Follow lockout procedure before servicing.&lt;/howtoavoid>
